aka.jmetadata.main

Class AbstractStreamJMetadata

  • java.lang.Object
    • aka.jmetadata.main.AbstractJMetadata
      • aka.jmetadata.main.AbstractStreamJMetadata
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JMetadataAudio, JMetadataChapter, JMetadataMenu, JMetadataSubtitle, JMetadataVideo

    public abstract class AbstractStreamJMetadata
extends AbstractJMetadata
    AbstractStreamJMetadata is an abstract class providing commons methods for metadata extraction.
    The developer need only subclass this abstract class and add, if necessary, specific methods.
    Author:
    Charlotte
